<h2 class="header">Description</h2>Learning Spanish specifically <div class="desc" style="display: none;">for the workplace is now possible thanks to a highly effective method designed for people without countless hours to spend learning another language. <br />
By strategically helping you memorize key phrases, vocabulary and expressions in your speciality, MosaLingua gives you the tools to naturally speak Spanish in a professional context. And with its integrated dialogues, the app exposes you to business Spanish, naturally improving your oral comprehension and speaking skills. <br />
<br />
► Tested and praised by many website and blogs<br />
► Reviewed by over 6,000 users, with an average score of 4.5/5!<br />
<br />
AN EFFICIENT, PRAGMATIC AND USEFUL APPROACH TO PREPARE FOR A PROFESSIONAL SETTING<br />
► Easily express yourself over the phone<br />
► Write emails<br />
► Socialize with partners, colleagues and clients<br />
► Lead or participate in a meeting<br />
► Make a CV and succeed at a job interview<br />
► Negotiate<br />
► Participate at a public event, expo, conference, etc.<br />
► Motivate a team<br />
► Lead a project<br />
<br />
CONTENT THAT TARGETS THE SPECIALIZED VOCABULARY OF YOUR FIELD<br />
► Customer service<br />
► Human resources<br />
► Sales/purchasing<br />
► Finances, accounting<br />
► Advertising, marketing<br />
► Information technology<br />
► Logistics, production<br />
► Management, administration<br />
<br />
A HIGHLY EFFECTIVE LEARNING METHOD BASED ON RESEARCH<br />
MosaLingua Business Spanish uses the spaced repetition system. See the video here: http://mosalingua.com<br />
► learn business Spanish with a concrete, effective method: each revision flashcard is predetermined according to your specific difficulties<br />
► stop wasting time: spend more time on what’s useful and stop spending time on what you already know<br />
► constantly adapts to your issues and according to your speed (it’s like having a personal Spanish professor in your pocket!)<br />
► uses your audio and visual memory<br />
► reinforced concrete learning (long-term memorization)<br />
<br />
MOBILE LEARNING (GREAT FOR VACATION OR COMMUTES)<br />
► Spanish sessions of varying durations (whether you have 2 or 30 minutes free)<br />
► automatically adjust towards your speed and where you have difficulties<br />
► no need for an Internet connection; it’s all offline!<br />
<br />
CONTENT<br />
► more than 2,500 cards containing words and phrases pronounced by native speakers<br />
► numerous suggestions written by experts to help you in your professional life, along with numerous language tips<br />
► 18 main categories (finding a job, on the phone, letters/emails, meetings, presentations, sales, marketing, finances, etc.)<br />
► over 100 specialized categories (breaking the ice, writing an agenda or the minutes of a meeting, organizing a work dinner, etc.) <br />
► 10 available levels, covering key skills for the Spanish of your profession)<br />
► 7 dialogues of the most common situations in the workplace<br />
► More than 100 bonuses to unlock<br />
► online Spanish dictionary<br />
► (exclusive) ability to add your own flashcards<br />
<br />
MosaLingua Business Spanish is ideal for those with a basic level of Spanish and/or those who want to target Spanish in a professional context. If you are a total beginner, we recommend you our general Spanish app, MosaLingua Spanish. <br />
<br />
<br />
The app constantly evolves: we implement the comments, suggestions and needs of our users and schedule regular updates for free!<br />
If you need any help or have a suggestion, please use the support link below – response guaranteed!</div>
